cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a training algorithm for modular networks that can be applied to both image recognition and language modeling tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper involves the use of neural networks, which suggests the sub-categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as possible categories.
